						               													<description>Puffing Gods'' is a card game where players interpret different primitive leaders of completely mad tribes that uses their villagers to send their offerings to the &amp;quot;Mystery Hill&amp;quot; in a frantic race to please their gods. When the all-mighty receive their gifts in his kingdom, the player is rewarded with divine benefits. However, in that fervor, your flock decreases and you will have to convert the villagers of the surrounding tribes to be ahead. Be sure to send your offering before someone does.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is played among 3 to 6 players and consists of a hand draft gameplay. Players need to place villagers in their play area adding later some &amp;quot;task&amp;quot; cards to make them prepare the offerings, to later on, play a ritual card to send the offerings to one of the three gods available. As soon the gods are satisfied with a specific amount of offerings they reward the player with special benefits and score points for him. Different gods with unique powers grant the player interaction and fast-paced game play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
